@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yvpbiv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.03 + tmp + 0.86)))
    v1 = 0.60
    v0 = 0.50
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.exp(tmp + 0.65)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.54 + v0 + 0.45) / (v0 + 0.61 / v2 + 0.95)))
    v0 = wp.sin((0.06 - wp.sin(v0 + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
